title: MASK Disc 1
description:
This is Disc 1 of the 80's cartoon series Mobile Armored Strike Kommand (M.A.S.K.)

The file size is due to it being VOB (DVD 9) format.  I'll try this first disc out as is to see if anyone likes the quality.  Please comment and let me know if it turned out ok.

If anyone knows how to break this down to a smaller file for ease of download, please tell me.
